{"word":"G3373 - μηκύνω - mēkýnō - may-koo'-no - Grow up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μηκύνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mēkýnō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">may-koo'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Grow up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"நீளமாக்கு - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"to make long, to lengthen"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3372 - μῆκος - mēkos - may'-kos/3372\">G3372</a>; to <i>lengthen</i>, that is, (middle voice) to <i>enlarge:</i> - grow up.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}